text: "Paper Plane" is a 1972 song by British rock band Status Quo. It was taken from their fifth studio album Piledriver. It went to number 8 in the United Kingdom, number 11 in Ireland and number 42 in Germany. In 2007, it was covered by Persephone's Bees. Category:1972 songs Category:Status Quo songs
